description:
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Doom 1 &amp; 2 Megawads Volume 1 &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;


This is a collection of all the level megawads I've managed to find through Google, /idgames Archives, websites, etc. I just thought I would bundle them all together in one convenient download, so here ya go. I will release a Volume 2 once I manage to dig up more, which is very likely. If you prefer to use an OS port, I would highly suggest either GZDoom or Zandronum. GZDoom has a more up-to-date version of OpenGL, but Zandronum offers online play. Enjoy, and play Brutal Doom while you're at it :P


&gt;&gt; GZDoom Instructions &lt;&lt;

1.) Unzip you desired megawad, and drag &amp; drop it onto the GZDoom icon.
2.) Select either Doom or Doom 2 in the menu, depending on which game the wad was made for.

&gt;&gt; Zandronum Instructions &lt;&lt;

1.) Inside the Zandronum folder, create a folder called &quot;skins&quot;.
2.) Unzip the desired megawad, and place it inside the 'skins' folder.&quot;
3.) Click on the zandronum icon, and select either Doom or Doom 2 in the menu, depending on which game the wad was designed for.
